34:41.941 --> 34:44.151
Yeah, that looks good.

34:44.220 --> 34:46.601
Cool.

34:46.670 --> 34:49.846
I'm not out here doing this
because I'm afraid of failure.

34:49.915 --> 34:51.917
I'm doing it because
there's something worthwhile

34:51.986 --> 34:53.263
that I wanna gain.

34:56.956 --> 34:59.373
Yeah, so now that I've,
I've got my tent kind

34:59.442 --> 35:00.546
of rebuilt here.

35:00.615 --> 35:02.928
I do have a nice,
flat, even floor.

35:02.997 --> 35:05.517
So, I'm gonna get my sled
