36:51.243 --> 36:54.039
Their little brains are
soaking up so much knowledge.

36:54.108 --> 36:56.766
Learning about gathering
resource through the ice.

36:56.835 --> 36:58.319
They're getting to
learn a little bit

36:58.388 --> 37:01.011
about chopping firewood.

