With the windchill,
it's around negative 70.

39:16.423 --> 39:18.632
So if this caribou hide
works in these temperatures,

39:18.701 --> 39:20.461
it's definitely gonna work in,

39:20.530 --> 39:22.636
in any other
temperature I see out here.

39:25.673 --> 39:26.674
Cool.

39:26.743 --> 39:28.711
Just like that, there's water.

39:28.780 --> 39:29.884
It's clean.

39:29.953 --> 39:32.024
It didn't take long
to get through,

39:32.093 --> 39:34.613
so I would definitely
say this was a success.

