39:39.653 --> 39:40.999
middle of summer.

39:41.068 --> 39:43.622
You just adapt
to those changes.

39:43.691 --> 39:46.798
Some for you Java.

39:46.867 --> 39:48.627
Some for me.

39:48.696 --> 39:50.146
You work with nature.

39:50.215 --> 39:52.493
You figure out how to do it,
